&lt;h2 id="stormbolt-to-the-face--gentle-wc3">&lt;strong>Stormbolt to the FACE – Gentle WC3&amp;rsquo;s Avatar Commission&lt;/strong>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Awesome player, streamer, and all-around good human, &lt;strong>Gentle&lt;/strong> reached out for a custom WC3 Champions avatar—and I couldn’t have been happier to answer the call.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>He was super kind and professional throughout, and one thing that really made this commission special was the involvement of his girlfriend. She&amp;rsquo;s an artist too, and the piece she created for him was not only fantastic but &lt;em>hugely inspiring&lt;/em> as I explored the right angle and energy for the Mountain King.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Backgrounds for WCR Replay Generator</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/esports/backgrounds-for-wcr-replay-generator/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2009 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/esports/backgrounds-for-wcr-replay-generator/</guid><description>&lt;p>These are backgrounds for the WCReplays.com replay generator.&lt;/p>
